"title": "4190: spiritism",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4190: spiritism",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The use of mediums or other spiritual intermediaries to communicate with the dead. Scripture forbids such practices, which are inconsistent with obedience to a living God.</p>\n<h2>Spiritism forbidden by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:31\">LEV 19:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:10-Deut18:12\">DEU 18:10–18:12</a></p>\n<h2>Punishment for spiritism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:27\">LEV 20:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:6\">LEV 20:6</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritism practised in Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:6\">2KI 21:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:6\">2CH 33:6</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:4-1Sam28:20\">1SA 28:4–28:20</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritists expelled from Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:24\">2KI 23:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:3\">1SA 28:3</a></p>\n<h2>The futility of spiritism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:19\">ISA 8:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:2-Isa19:3\">ISA 19:2–19:3</a></p>",
